    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term chassis integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the VANOS system has been recently serviced to maintain optimal variable valve timing. The suspension geometry is enhanced with upgraded bushings and dampers, providing precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor signs of use consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and drivetrain remain in excellent health, having undergone a recent valve clearance adjustment. A turn-key performance icon for the technical driver.",
